y dopants such as Cr, Mn, V and Cu may be\ncorrelated with the suppression of nematic fluctuations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 May 2019 05:04:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-13"}
