alized to systems\nwith a larger number of graphene layers, indicating that multilayer graphene\nsandwiched between two hydrogenated graphene is a versatile material that can\nbe used in QSHE, sensor devices, etc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 May 2019 06:41:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 Jul 2019 07:44:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 4 Oct 2019 10:10:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-07"}
