rage of more than 99 percent of the words used\nin popular newspapers, and restore vowels in words (out of context) simply and\nefficiently.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 May 2019 10:14:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-13"}
