c variant of Herbrand's theorem, which reduces the\nsemantic entailment of a logic-programming query by a program to the search of\na suitable answer substitution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 May 2019 12:59:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-13"}
