terface for the as bonded samples. This amorphous layer is\ncrystallized upon annealing, leading to the high TBC found in our work. Our\nwork paves the way for thermal transport across bonded interfaces, which will\nimpact real-world applications of semiconductor integration and packaging.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 May 2019 13:43:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-13"}
